{
  "name": "Self-Healing Error Handler",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "sticky-instructions",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.sticky",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        100,
        -250
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 550,
        "height": 220,
        "content": "### 🛠️ SELF-HEALING ERROR HANDLER SOP\nThis workflow captures execution failures across your n8n instance and executes automated recovery runs.\n\n#### 🔑 Required Credentials:\n- **n8n REST API Key**: Access to retrieve, manage, and retry failed executions via `/api/v1`.\n- **OAuth Server Client Credentials**: Key/secret to refresh expired tokens if necessary.\n- **Slack & Discord Webhook**: Channels to post healed summaries or escalate hard crashes.\n\n#### ⚙️ Configuration Variables:\n- `N8N_API_KEY`: API key with admin rights to retry executions.\n- `N8N_URL`: Internal URL of the self-hosted n8n instance (e.g. `http://localhost:5678` or `https://n8n.your-domain.com`).\n\n#### 🧪 Testing Protocol:\n1. Configure this workflow's Settings to NOT listen to itself to prevent infinite error loops.\n2. Create a test workflow with a failed node (e.g., calling an invalid URL) and trigger it.\n3. Verify this handler catches the error, parses metadata, and routes to appropriate branch.\n4. Verify rate-limited runs cooldown and successfully retry.\n\n---\n*Upsell Note: To request Done-For-You custom RevOps & Pipeline Strategy or advanced n8n setups, connect with our automation architects at whoisalfaz.me.*"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "error-trigger",
      "name": "Error Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.errorTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        0,
        0
      ],
      "parameters": {}
    },
    {
      "id": "extract-error-details",
      "name": "Extract Error Details",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        250,
        0
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const errorData = $input.item.json;\nreturn {\n  execution_id: errorData.execution?.id || \"N/A\",\n  execution_url: errorData.execution?.url || \"N/A\",\n  workflow_id: errorData.workflow?.id || \"N/A\",\n  workflow_name: errorData.workflow?.name || \"N/A\",\n  error_message: errorData.error?.message || \"N/A\",\n  error_stack: errorData.error?.stack || \"N/A\",\n  failed_node: errorData.node?.name || \"N/A\",\n  failed_node_type: errorData.node?.type || \"N/A\"\n};"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "classify-error-type",
      "name": "Classify Error Type",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.switch",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        500,
        0
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "rules": {
          "rules": [
            {
              "value": "token",
              "operation": "contains"
            },
            {
              "value": "429",
              "operation": "contains"
            },
            {
              "value": "",
              "operation": "isEmpty"
            }
          ]
        },
        "dataType": "string",
        "value1": "={{ $json.error_message.toLowerCase() }}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "trigger-oauth-refresh",
      "name": "Trigger OAuth Refresh",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        750,
        -200
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://your-auth-server.com/oauth/token",
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "grant_type",
              "value": "refresh_token"
            },
            {
              "name": "refresh_token",
              "value": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "retry-execution-auth",
      "name": "Retry Execution (Auth)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1000,
        -200
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "=http://localhost:5678/api/v1/executions/{{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.execution_id }}/retry",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "headers": {
          "parameter": [
            {
              "name": "X-N8N-API-KEY",
              "value": "YOUR_N8N_API_KEY_HERE"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "slack-healed-alert-auth",
      "name": "Slack Healed Alert (Auth)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.slack",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1250,
        -200
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "channel": "#ops-alerts",
        "text": "🛠️ *Self-Healing Action Taken* \nAuth/Token error detected on workflow *{{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.workflow_name }}* (Node: *{{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.failed_node }}*). \n\n✅ Token refresh triggered and execution retried."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "wait-60s",
      "name": "Wait 60s",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.wait",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        750,
        0
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "amount": 60,
        "unit": "seconds"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "retry-execution-rate-limit",
      "name": "Retry Execution (Rate Limit)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1000,
        0
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "=http://localhost:5678/api/v1/executions/{{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.execution_id }}/retry",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "headers": {
          "parameter": [
            {
              "name": "X-N8N-API-KEY",
              "value": "YOUR_N8N_API_KEY_HERE"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "slack-healed-alert-rate",
      "name": "Slack Healed Alert (Rate)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.slack",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1250,
        0
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "channel": "#ops-alerts",
        "text": "🛠️ *Self-Healing Action Taken* \nRate Limit (429) detected on workflow *{{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.workflow_name }}* (Node: *{{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.failed_node }}*). \n\n✅ Wait cooldown complete and execution retried."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "log-to-postgres-dlq",
      "name": "Log to Postgres DLQ",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        750,
        200
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://your-dlq-endpoint.com/dlq",
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "execution_id",
              "value": "={{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.execution_id }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "workflow_name",
              "value": "={{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.workflow_name }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "error_message",
              "value": "={{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.error_message }}"
            },
            {
              "name": "execution_url",
              "value": "={{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.execution_url }}"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "send-discord-alert",
      "name": "Send Discord Alert",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1000,
        200
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "YOUR_DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL_HERE",
        "sendBody": true,
        "bodyParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "content",
              "value": "🚨 **Manual Escalation required: Workflow Hard Failure!** \n\n**Workflow:** {{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.workflow_name }} \n**Node:** {{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.failed_node }} \n**Error:** {{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.error_message }} \n\n[Inspect n8n Execution log]({{ $('extract-error-details').item.json.execution_url }})"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Error Trigger": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Extract Error Details",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Extract Error Details": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Classify Error Type",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Classify Error Type": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Trigger OAuth Refresh",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "node": "Wait 60s",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ],
        [
          {
            "node": "Log to Postgres DLQ",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Trigger OAuth Refresh": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Retry Execution (Auth)",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Retry Execution (Auth)": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Slack Healed Alert (Auth)",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Wait 60s": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Retry Execution (Rate Limit)",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Retry Execution (Rate Limit)": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Slack Healed Alert (Rate)",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    },
    "Log to Postgres DLQ": {
      "main": [
        [
          {
            "node": "Send Discord Alert",
            "type": "main",
            "index": 0
          }
        ]
      ]
    }
  },
  "settings": {},
  "meta": {}
}
